comment.body:
@Kaffie The people that have interest in decentralization are basically divided in few groups:
1- the group of technology enthusiasts that have to try every new technology; 
2- the group against government abuses that supports individual freedom;
3- and the group of people that want to share illegal contents. 
I'm pretty sure the second group is way larger but the first group is more likely to discover and use new technologies as ZeroNet, so at this time most users are a mix of first and second group.
